title: syntax
pid: 065ff7fe-53c3-4182-83c0-dcd8e35eda2b
body: |2-
  // Note that "type" below is a keyword.
  switch v := i.(type) {
    case T:
      // here v has type T
    case S:
      // here v has type S
    default:
      // no match; here v is equal to i in type and value
      // (but [[id:12f2e827-dcb1-4adf-b7a8-2d946fcdb7ae][it might be a copy]]).
  }
contains:
- 12f2e827-dcb1-4adf-b7a8-2d946fcdb7ae
